<p>Namenda kept her from deteriorating for 4 yrs. Now, I see a slight change, but she is still doing well. I believe Namenda has a lot to do with it. Several caregivers at the various support group I attended over 4 yrs also reported marked improvement in their loved ones. I am an internist, geriatrician and Hospice doctor, so I have been working with AD patients and families for about 30 years now.</p>
